    {
        "content": "<p>Okay, that's what I figured. I was trying to see if I could derive (for example) <code>has_deriv_within_at f (f' y) t y</code> from <code>has_deriv_within_at f (f' y) s y</code> given <code>s ‚äÜ t</code> but have not been successful.</p>",
